The build failed during the `%prep` stage because the directory extracted from the source tarball is `oterm-0.13.0`, but the spec file attempts to change directory into `oterm_0.13.0` (using an underscore instead of a hyphen).

To fix this, update the `%setup` or `%autosetup` macro in the `.spec` file to explicitly specify the correct directory name using the `-n` flag.

Change:
`%setup -q` (or similar)
to:
`%setup -q -n oterm-0.13.0`